<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><author>Sobir Umurov</author>
<title>Sevgisidir abadiy</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Xudo uchun ketgan vakting
 Bu sening katta baxting
 Kel, titrok-la xuzuriga
 Ruhing yashnar nur ichra

[C1]
   Sevgisidir abadiy, farmonlari mukammal
   Gar amrini kullasang, bol kabi shirin-asal
   Bitmas, tuganmas boylik, donolikning manbayi
   Sen Uzingsan Otajon, etay Suzingga amal

[V2]
 Yashaysan Ruxing ila, mudom kalbim yoritib
 Fakat Senga topinib, sirim, orzuyim ochib
 Yuragimning tubi emas, turi Sen uchun tayyor
 Rabbim kelib shoxlik kilgin, bilsin borlik Seni</lyrics>
</song>